workflow.name: Classify & process IT requests with Jotform, Gemini AI and Google Workspace
workflow.description:
# Who‚Äôs it for

This workflow is perfect for IT departments, helpdesk teams, or internal service units that manage incoming support requests through Jotform. It automates ticket handling, classification, and response‚Äîsaving time and ensuring consistent communication.

# How it works

When a new IT service request is submitted through Jotform, this workflow automatically triggers in n8n. The submitted details (name, department, category, comments, etc.) are structured and analyzed using Google Gemini AI to summarize and classify the issue‚Äôs priority level (P0‚ÄìP2).

P0 (High): Urgent issues that send an immediate Telegram alert.

P1 (Medium) / P2 (Low): Logged in Google Sheets for tracking and reporting.

After classification, the workflow sends a confirmation email to the requester via Gmail, providing a summary of their submission and current status.

# How to set up
- Connect your Jotform account to the Jotform Trigger node.
- Add your Google Sheets, Gmail, and (optionally) Telegram credentials.
- Map your Jotform fields in the ‚ÄúSet‚Äù node (Full Name, Department, Category, etc.).
- Test by submitting a form response.

# Requirements
- Jotform account and published IT request form
- Google Sheets account
- Gmail account (for replies)
- Optional: Telegram bot for real-time alerts
- n8n account (cloud or self-hosted)

# How to customize the workflow
- Adjust AI classification logic in the Priority Classifier node.
- Modify email templates for tone or format.
- Add filters or additional routing for different departments.
- Extend to integrate with your internal ticketing or Slack systems.

parameters.content:
## Form

Starts workflow when a new IT Service Request is submitted on Jotform.

Captures: Full Name, Department, Email, Building Number, Problem Category, and Comments.

Connects to ‚ÄúSet Fields‚Äù node for structured data mapping.

## Summarizaion & Classifer

- Uses AI to summarize problem details for reports and alerts.
- Works with Google Gemini model for summarization and classification.
- Produces a short ‚ÄúSummary‚Äù used in Sheets, emails, and Telegram messages.
- Analyzes request details (problem + comments).

### Classifies into:
P0 (High) ‚Äì Immediate action
P1 (Medium) ‚Äì Affects single user
P2 (Low) ‚Äì Non-critical maintenance

Routes to correct Google Sheet tab and notification channel.

## Automate IT Service Request intake ‚Üí classification ‚Üí storage ‚Üí notification ‚Üí acknowledgment.

- Faster IT response time
- Centralized data in Google Sheets
- AI-driven ticket summarization
- Automatic priority routing and communication
